            <div class="title">
                Money Resolutions (Government Proposals)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1937-11-09/debates/98cb7c14-1a74-431d-99b4-065efa093107/PublicHealth(Coal-MineRefuse)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
