<p class="">May I ask the Prime Minister now that Second Readings are to be taken before Financial Resolutions, whether it is intended, when the main purpose of a Bill is to incur expenditure, that the Clauses containing expenditure are to be printed in italics?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
